<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1319220-is-this-a-pretty-typical-book-for-the">Is this a pretty typical book for the series (it&#39;s #1) or do they get better? I ask since, so far, I haven&#39;t liked this one.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1319220'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F44230.The_Silver_Pigs">like</a></span>

</li>
